title: Bradford Bishop // 60
description:
In 1976, a family of 5 was found brutally murdered, their bodies set on fire and left in the woods nearly 300 miles from their home in Maryland. The number one suspect in the case has been on the run ever since. This is the story of Bradford Bishop.
